API name: Predix Parking Planning Streaming API v1
Description: The Parking Planning API offers parking metadata obtained from lighting sensors in parking lots and along public roadways. Information such as real time occupancy status is available. This REST API returns data in JSON format, and uses OAuth 2 and Tokens for authentication. Predix is an industrial software platform developed by General Electric Digital which aims to improve asset performance management (APM), operations, and business.
